install path of 'Driver' is wrong.
that shoud be 'PEARDIR/Image/Transform/Driver'.

How-To-Repeat: <?php
	require_once 'Image/Transform.php';

	$img =& Image_Transform::factory('GD');
	if (PEAR::isError($img)) {
		echo $img->getMessage();
	}
?>
